headline: Nobu Hotel Caesars New Orleans opens at Harrah’s redevelopment
summary: The Nobu hotel at Caesars’ $435 million resort and casino project marks the pair’s third collab and debuts amid Caesars’ nationwide expansion.

headline: Hail, Caesars! The Casino Stock Could Get a Super Boost From the Super Bowl.
